name: The Spider - Jordy
description:
Nocturnal Pastel - Jordy
Shedding light on creatures that play in the dark 

Belonging to the magic of the night, darkness is no obstacle for the nocturnal Spider. It is said that when spider webs unite, they can tie down a lion. 

Visit original edit in the neenTAE collection on opensea (Part 2 of Nocturnal Bottone)
